OL,3,CPolice Chief Constable's suspension
OL,4,Clifted
OL,6,FThe suspension of Gloucestershire
OL,7,FPolice's Chief Constable, Rod Hansen,
OL,8,Fhas been lifted after a "change in
OL,9,Fcircumstances" - but will still be
OL,10,Finvestigated by a police watchdog.
OL,12,FHansen has been redeployed in a non
OL,13,Fpublic-facing role elsewhere in the
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FIt follows his suspension by the force
OL,17,Fon 7 October last year after being
OL,18,Fissued with a gross misconduct notice
OL,19,Fby the Independent Office for Police
OL,20,FConduct (IOPC).
