OL,3,CPolice Chief Constable's suspension
OL,4,Clifted
OL,6,FThe IOPC is continuing to investigate
OL,7,Fthe allegations in which both Hansen
OL,8,Fand his chief of staff Gary Thompson
OL,9,Fwere both suspended by the Police and
OL,10,FCrime Commissioner, Chris Nelson.
OL,12,FMr Nelson has since lifted the
OL,13,Fsuspension and said: "On Monday,
OL,14,FOctober 7, 2024, I suspended
OL,15,FGloucestershire's Chief Constable Rod
OL,16,FHansen pending an IOPC investigation
OL,17,Finto an alleged breach of standards of
OL,18,Fprofessional behaviour, which if
OL,19,Fproved could be gross misconduct.
OL,26,@uD@VOU
