OL,3,CPolice Chief Constable's suspension
OL,4,Clifted
OL,6,F"I am required to review this decision
OL,7,Fevery 28 days. I have recently
OL,8,Fcompleted the latest review, and have
OL,9,Fagreed that this suspension must now
OL,10,Fbe lifted as the grounds for it are no
OL,11,Flonger met, following a change in
OL,12,Fcircumstances.
OL,14,F"Since I made my original decision,
OL,15,Fthe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,16,F(NPCC) has offered Mr Hansen a
OL,17,Fredeployment to a non-public facing
OL,18,Frole, outside Gloucestershire. This
OL,19,Fredeployment was effective from
OL,20,FWednesday 8 January.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
