OL,3,CPolice Chief Constable's suspension
OL,4,Clifted
OL,6,F"It does not affect the IOPC
OL,7,Finvestigation, which is continuing, or
OL,8,Fthe current position in the
OL,9,FConstabulary.
OL,11,F"Temporary Chief Constable Maggie
OL,12,FBlyth remains in her role, and day to
OL,13,Fday policing continues as usual."
OL,15,FThe investigation centres on the
OL,16,Fhandling, by both individuals, of an
OL,17,Fallegation of computer misuse and a
OL,18,Fpotential data breach by another
OL,19,Fmember of staff.
