OL,6,FThe probe aims to ascertain whether
OL,7,Frelevant policies and procedures were
OL,8,Fsubsequently followed.
OL,10,FThe constabulary has been asked for an
OL,11,Fupdate on Mr Thompson and whether he
OL,12,Fhas also seen his suspension lifted
OL,13,Fand offered redeployment elsewhere but
OL,14,Fthe force declined to comment.
OL,16,F"For privacy and operational reasons,
OL,17,Fwe do not comment on individual
OL,18,Femployment matters," a Gloucestershire
OL,19,FConstabulary spokesperson said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@TO]
