OL,6,F"Our stance remains consistent with
OL,7,Fprevious statements, and there is no
OL,8,Ffurther information to share at this
OL,9,Ftime."
OL,11,FAn IOPC spokesperson said: "Our
OL,12,Finvestigation into the conduct of
OL,13,FChief Constable Hansen remains ongoing.
OL,15,F"Suspension is a matter for the
OL,16,Femployer, in this instance the Police
OL,17,Fand Crime Commissioner for
OL,18,FGloucestershire."
